description: Mephisto keeps pulling Blaze's strings, and manipulation remains atop the menue. With Alejandra catching a ride to an orbiting space station, the spirit of Vengeance begins to whisper sweet nothings. Now with everything on the line, Sin that is, Blaze must decide to keep Mephisto in power or risk living like a zombie.

description: Translates World War Hulk Prologue: World Breaker & Incredible Hulk #106.

Sometimes you have to go for broke. Take the would-be bank robbers of Scott Morse's Spaghetti Western: an old man with a terminal illness and his aimless young friend. Convinced modern convenience has edged out all the cowboy rebels, the duo descends upon a California savings and loan, ready to take the rich "fatcats" for all they're worth. And then the fun begins.

An out of print OGN homage to the Spaghetti Western
